Package de.dfki.dmas.owls2wsdl.utils Description

Contains helper classes and all extras needed. E.g. WSDL2JavaWrapper class to Axis WSDL2Java tool (needed for complete top down approach: OWL-S 2 WSDL 2 Java).

Related Documentation

For more information see:
  • http://projects.semwebcentral.org/projects/owls2wsdl/
  • http://www-ags.dfki.uni-sb.de/~klusch/i2a/html/software.html
  • http://www.htw-saarland.de/Members/fourman/thesis/
